---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Us - AIPlatformDataSecurity">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Ready to Join Our Global Community?</p>
  </div>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="contact-intro">
      <h2>Get Connected</h2>
      <p>
        Ready to take your IT security career to the next level? Join our global community of professionals who are committed to continuous learning and constructive feedback. Remember, you need to have thick skin and be prepared for direct, honest criticism.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-methods">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>üîó LinkedIn</h3>
        <p>Connect with our official LinkedIn page for updates, networking, and community news.</p>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/31300296" target="_blank" class="contact-link">
          Visit Our LinkedIn Page
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>üìã Registration Form</h3>
        <p>Fill out our registration form to express your interest in joining our community.</p>
        <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1hvP3jMDt5S7UFub0t-48V2ALb_opJOixBRWX0uHHXf4/viewform?pli=1&pli=1&edit_requested=true" target="_blank" class="contact-link">
          Complete Registration Form
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-card">
        <h3>üì∫ YouTube Channel</h3>
        <p>Subscribe to our YouTube channel for educational content and community discussions.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@CloudandDevOpsBabies" target="_blank" class="contact-link">
          Subscribe to Our Channel
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="requirements-section">
      <h2>Before You Join</h2>
      <div class="requirements-grid">
        <div class="requirement-card">
          <h3>üí™ Thick Skin Required</h3>
          <p>Our community provides direct, honest feedback that can be harsh but constructive. You must be prepared to receive criticism without taking it personally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="requirement-card">
          <h3>üéØ No Ego Policy</h3>
          <p>Leave your ego at the door. Everyone in our community is learning, and being humble is essential for growth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="requirement-card">
          <h3>üìö Commitment to Learning</h3>
          <p>You must be committed to following our learning schedule and participating actively in discussions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="requirement-card">
          <h3>üåç Global Perspective</h3>
          <p>Be prepared to interact with professionals from around the world with diverse backgrounds and approaches.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="moderator-contact">
      <h2>Meet Our Moderator</h2>
      <div class="moderator-info">
        <h3>Joe M - "JoeVirus"</h3>
        <p>
          Joe M is our community moderator and the driving force behind AIPlatformDataSecurity. 
          His philosophy is simple: <strong>"You are as good as your last movie. Keep your brags fresh."</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          Joe maintains high standards and expects the same from all community members. 
          His direct communication style has helped hundreds of professionals grow their careers.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joem75/" target="_blank" class="moderator-link">
          Connect with Joe on LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do I join the WhatsApp group?</h3>
          <p>Complete our registration form and connect with us on LinkedIn. We'll review your application and reach out if you're a good fit for our community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What should I expect from the community?</h3>
          <p>Expect direct, honest feedback on your work and learning progress. The criticism can be harsh but is always constructive and aimed at helping you improve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is there a cost to join?</h3>
          <p>No, joining our community is completely free. We believe in accessible education and professional development.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What topics are covered in the group?</h3>
          <p>We cover a wide range of IT security topics including cloud security, DevOps, platform engineering, and career development.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--gradient-tertiary);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: slideInDown 0.8s ease-out;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.3);
  }

  @keyframes slideInDown {
    from {
      transform: translateY(-50px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-intro {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-intro h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
    animation-fill-mode: both;
  }

  .contact-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .contact-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .contact-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      transform: translateY(30px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .contact-card h3 {
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .contact-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gradient-secondary);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(240, 147, 251, 0.4);
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    background: var(--gradient-success);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(67, 233, 123, 0.6);
  }

  .requirements-section {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .requirements-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .requirements-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .requirement-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: slideInLeft 0.6s ease-out;
    animation-fill-mode: both;
  }

  .requirement-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .requirement-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .requirement-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .requirement-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  .requirement-card:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
    border-color: var(--secondary-accent);
  }

  @keyframes slideInLeft {
    from {
      transform: translateX(-30px);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .requirement-card h3 {
    background: var(--gradient-secondary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .requirement-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .moderator-contact {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .moderator-contact h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .moderator-info {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .moderator-info h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .moderator-info p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .moderator-link {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gradient-success);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(67, 233, 123, 0.4);
  }

  .moderator-link:hover {
    background: var(--gradient-tertiary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(56, 249, 215, 0.6);
  }

  .faq-section {
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--bg-color);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .contact-methods {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .requirements-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>